dsDescriptionValue.value: The dataset is originally downloaded from UCI repository https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Indoor+User+Movement+Prediction+from+RSS+data We organized it into a csv format for machine learning indoor User Movement Prediction from RSS dataset contains time-series generated by a Wireless Sensor Network (WSN) deployed in real-world office environments. The binary classification task consists in predicting the pattern of user movements
